{
  "stem": "14708.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went-- this was a very beautiful spring Sunday morning, and we went for a walk.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I came home, and I told my mother, I met a boy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He's quite different than anybody else I know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Yeah, so this was the beginning, and then Jan started to come to our house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we heard the first time-- we knew that there were deportations from Czechoslovakia already, from 1941, '42.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We knew that and of course what is happening in Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But somehow, the Hungarian Jews were incredibly naive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they always, always said the regent, Horthy, won't let us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Nothing will happen to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they always thought about themselves as Hungarians, so nothing can happen to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And Jan told us the stories from his home and from his family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he said already then that probably nobody is alive by now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we heard from him the first time about the-- about the false papers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he said that this is the only way how to save-- how to try at least to save yourself.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because there were some people who tried to convert.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My father didn't want to hear about that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then there were some rumors that they are taking only young girls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But if the girls are married, they don't take married women.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So there were lots of quick, quick, quick marriages.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And Jan laughed when he heard that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He said that that's nonsense, nothing like this is going help.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Have papers and try to escape till it is time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Now, this was very difficult to convince my father because he said I never did anything illegal in my life, and I don't want these papers in my house, and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "My mother was more understanding.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
